Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.77,0:01:27.73,lassie episode,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:82770,87734}{\blur0.5\fad(300,0)\pos(320,290)}My Father's Salary
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.49,0:01:40.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:96492,100246}What's that? She started\Nto drink milk on her own?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.24,0:01:41.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:100246,101497}I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.49,0:01:44.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:101497,104250}Lassie, you have to grow big.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.63,0:01:50.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:108630,110715}Hey now, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.71,0:01:51.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:110715,111966}W-What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.96,0:01:53.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:111966,113176}It's her teeth.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:113176,114052}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.05,0:01:56.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:114052,116304}Lassie grew fangs.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.30,0:02:00.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:116304,120350}They're so small…\NThey're small, but they are there!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.77,0:02:14.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:132779,134030}Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.90,0:02:18.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:134906,138076}Just because you were bullied as a puppy,\Nyou shouldn't do the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.07,0:02:19.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138076,139410}Leave it alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.83,0:02:24.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142830,144957}Oh, boy. Look at yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.00,0:02:30.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149003,150046}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.21,0:02:41.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:156219,161224}Really, what is so fun about running around\Nfrom dawn to dusk every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.22,0:02:42.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:161224,162433}John!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.22,0:02:46.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:163226,166437}Come back!\NIt's breakfast time!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.64,0:02:49.48,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168648,169482}See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.27,0:02:53.98,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170274,173986}Dad has it a bit easier in the mornings\Never since they hired more office workers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.94,0:02:57.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174946,177198}I wish they hired a few nurses\Nat the hospital, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.03,0:03:04.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180034,184664}She's already friends with the bowl.\NLooks like she'll grow big in no time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.66,0:03:09.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184664,189335}But don't eat too much at once, Lassie.\NLeave some for later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.33,0:03:14.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:189335,194507}Today is Dad's payday and\Ntomorrow is Mom's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.59,0:03:17.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196592,197427}Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.26,0:03:23.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:198261,203891}That's right. Maybe I'll go all out\Nand prepare a feast for my own birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:29.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:204517,209188}If there are no surprise patients, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.18,0:03:30.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:209188,210898}Don't expect too much, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.23,0:03:32.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:211232,212692}I know, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.69,0:03:37.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212692,217113}I always pray that the people\Nof Greenall Bridge are in good health.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.11,0:03:38.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:217113,218614}Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:42.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:218614,222285}And I'll pray that\Nyour prayers are heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.03,0:03:47.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224036,227832}Take care of the house. I'm going\Nto get some supplies for the dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.83,0:03:48.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:227832,228750}Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:232420,235131}All right, it's almost there.\NGet ready, gentlemen.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:00.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:238509,240470}Let's get going. Steady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.47,0:04:01.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:240470,241763}Easy for ya to say!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241763,244140}Show some enthusiasm, boys.\NToday's payday!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.14,0:04:09.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244140,249353}Show… enthusiasm… he said?\NToday's… payday, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.31,0:04:19.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256319,259697}Everyone is getting pretty\Nexcited, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.69,0:04:21.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:259697,261449}I don't know. What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.44,0:04:24.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261449,264410}I'm busy calculating\Neveryone's salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:29.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266537,269499}Y-You're right.\NBetter not to make a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:31.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269499,271167}Do you think I'm the type\Nwho makes mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.79,0:04:33.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:271793,273336}No, I didn't mean it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:35.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273336,275171}Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:39.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:275713,279383}In the end,\Nmy salary is at stake too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.38,0:04:41.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279383,281385}I'll do a proper job.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.09,0:04:43.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283095,283888}Coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.64,0:04:47.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:286641,287642}What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.64,0:04:49.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287642,289894}Not you. Get me Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.35,0:04:51.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:290353,291562}Mr. Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.56,0:04:53.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:291562,293648}He says he wants to talk to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.90,0:04:59.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:298903,299737}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:00.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299737,300863}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.86,0:05:04.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:300863,304659}I just received news from the bottom.\NThere's water in the second channel.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.65,0:05:05.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:304659,305535}Water?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306369,307328}How much?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:307328,309413}I don't know the details.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.12,0:05:14.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:310122,314544}I don't think it's anything serious,\Nbut it's better if we take a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.08,0:05:18.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:315086,318798}No one at the bottom\Nwants to drown if we hit a spring.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.79,0:05:20.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:318798,320007}Elroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:24.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320007,324011}You want to go down\Nwhen we're so busy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.01,0:05:25.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324011,325930}Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.93,0:05:29.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325930,329600}It's fine.\NI can take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.60,0:05:31.76,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:329600,331769}You can go. Be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.18,0:05:34.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333187,334230}Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.23,0:05:36.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:334230,336399}– What's with that runt's attitude?\N– It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.19,0:05:41.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:338192,341153}Mr. Carraclough\Nis so good-natured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.15,0:05:46.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341153,346909}We're both just office workers.\NHe should've let the miners deal with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.13,0:06:05.01,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361132,365011}Christ. "I'm so happy! I'm so glad!"\N"Today is our payday!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.01,0:06:05.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:365011,365845}Yes…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:14.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:370808,374770}All right, let's get going.\NSandy, are you seated well?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.98,0:06:17.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:375980,377189}Yeah! All set.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:18.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:377189,378399}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.11,0:06:26.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:384113,386574}The weather is so beautiful today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.57,0:06:29.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:386574,389493}Yes, better than I expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.49,0:06:33.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:389493,393581}The mine workers today get\Ntheir salary for their hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.58,0:06:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393581,396292}Everyone will want to celebrate\Nand will buy extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:40.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:397126,400212}Those who don't work\Nwon't get to eat anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.21,0:06:45.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400212,405217}but those who work hard\Nwill eat until they are full.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:49.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406969,409931}Hey, mister!\NOne little question!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.93,0:06:52.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409931,412642}Greenall Bridge\Nis straight ahead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.18,0:06:57.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413184,417355}Yes, that's right.\NYou're a merchant, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.35,0:07:00.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417355,420149}How is it over there?\NAre there many customers?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.77,0:07:07.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420775,427156}Better than usual.\NPeople just received their salaries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.74,0:07:10.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:427740,430660}I understand. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:434372,437667}Business today\Nwill be much better, indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:22.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:437667,442129}When the mine's payday comes,\Nmerchants come from everywhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.34,0:07:36.06,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:453349,456060}Look, Lassie.\NThere are so many stands.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:40.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:456894,460940}There are many farmers\Nwho sell tasty vegetables.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:43.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:460940,463818}I wonder what kind of food\NMom's gonna cook?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.81,0:07:46.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:463818,466570}I can't wait for dinner, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.95,0:08:00.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478958,480793}We're finally done for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.79,0:08:02.08,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:480793,482086}I'm gonna sleep like a log.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:06.25,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:484880,486257}When will you give it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:486590,488551}Wait, wait. Don't rush.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.55,0:08:13.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488551,493723}I've just finished calculating everything\Nand getting the money out of the safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.72,0:08:16.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:493723,496392}Hurry up, man!\NI'm not gonna wait here forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.39,0:08:17.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496392,497393}All right, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499437,500813}Group II, Weller.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.81,0:08:22.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:500813,502773}Weller, Weller…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:24.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:502773,504650}There you are.\N3 pounds and 10 shillings.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:28.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506110,508112}Group II, Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:30.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508112,510740}Hamilton. Hamilton…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.74,0:08:33.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:510740,513451}Well, here it is. Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.45,0:08:34.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513451,514744}Group II, Roger.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:48.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525337,528883}There's not that much of it.\NIt should hold up for some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.88,0:08:51.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528883,531177}All right, gentlemen,\Nyou can go up.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.17,0:08:55.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531177,535514}Get your salaries and\Nbuy good food for yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.51,0:08:57.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535514,537641}We'll stay and make extra sure\Nit won't burst.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.64,0:08:58.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:537641,538893}Right, Sam?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:08:59.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:538893,539727}Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.18,0:09:05.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540186,545232}What about you, buddy? Aren't you\Nlooking forward to the weekend?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.23,0:09:06.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:545232,546525}What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.52,0:09:07.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546525,547526}Well…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.52,0:09:12.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547526,552573}His daughter is coming to stay over with\Nhis freshly christened granddaughter.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.57,0:09:14.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:552573,554325}You runts always talk too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.32,0:09:15.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554325,555785}I think it's better\Nif you go see your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:555785,556911}Don't be stupid, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:556911,558496}I can take your place.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.20,0:09:24.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:559205,564418}I'm still green, but we stopped one leakage\Nthe other day, so I know the gist of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.41,0:09:25.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564418,565419}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565419,568005}I'll stay with him.\NIt'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:33.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:569340,573511}To be honest, I don't know\Nhow to thank you. I owe you one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.05,0:09:38.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:574053,578265}Don't take too long, guys.\NMelissa and John are waiting for you, Sam.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.26,0:09:39.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:578265,579183}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.69,0:09:54.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:591695,594115}Everything looks\Nso delicious, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.11,0:09:57.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594115,597451}But before we eat,\Nwe have to look for something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.07,0:10:00.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598077,600037}Maybe something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.03,0:10:01.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:600037,601831}What's up, lad?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.24,0:10:04.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602248,604500}Are you interested in silverware?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.50,0:10:07.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604500,607336}No, not really. Let's go, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.75,0:10:11.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609755,611507}Oh? You're Sandy's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.50,0:10:15.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611507,615845}Ah John, I've got these\Nfrom Lake Dartford.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.84,0:10:18.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:615845,618139}You can catch these in a lake?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:19.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:618139,619431}They look delicious, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.26,0:10:22.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:620266,622560}If you're looking for Sandy,\Nshe's with Grandpa over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:24.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:622560,624645}Sure. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624645,626272}Oh? What's your problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.27,0:10:27.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:626272,627898}John! Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.89,0:10:29.15,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627898,629150}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.15,0:10:31.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:629150,631026}Hello, John. Here, take this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.69,0:10:32.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:631694,632820}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.57,0:10:36.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633571,636282}Are you telling me you don't\Nwant a free watermelon? Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.28,0:10:37.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636282,637867}Not at all. Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:637867,640119}So it's just you and Lassie today?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.11,0:10:43.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:640119,643038}Yes. Dad hasn't returned yet,\Nso we went ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.03,0:10:45.45,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643038,645457}By the way, Sandy…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.45,0:10:46.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:645457,646667}Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:50.54,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646667,650546}What kind of present do you think\NI should give to my Mom on her birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.33,0:10:52.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651338,652464}Birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:53.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652923,653966}A present!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.25,0:10:56.46,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:654258,656468}Hey, Sandy! Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.55,0:10:58.38,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:656552,658387}Follow me! This way, this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:03.14,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:660514,663142}Take a look, gentlemen!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.14,0:11:09.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663142,669356}Give your wife one of these brooches\Nand it won't lose its shine for the lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:10.35,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669356,670357}I'll get one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.35,0:11:12.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670357,672526}You have a good eye,\Nmy good man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.52,0:11:13.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:672526,673194}See?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.19,0:11:14.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:673194,674236}Jewelry?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:17.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674737,677740}But I don't have\Nthis kind of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.74,0:11:20.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677740,680576}Why don't you buy it\Ntogether with your dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.57,0:11:21.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680576,681869}Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.86,0:11:24.12,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:681869,684121}Let's wait till Dad\Ncomes back, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:36.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:692922,696050}I'm so tired. I'm so tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.09,0:11:40.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:697092,700930}Now, let's go to the office\Nto get your salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.05,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700930,702056}Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:43.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:702723,703599}Elroy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:46.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704433,706810}He left before me… Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:51.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:708229,711398}"Mr. Carraclough,\Nyour salary is in the safe"?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:715277,717863}"I handed out salaries\Nto the rest of the employees".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.48,0:12:00.57,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718489,720574}But you still haven't\Nreceived yours, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.57,0:12:03.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720574,723160}I haven't. Does it take long?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.16,0:12:06.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:723160,726997}No, not at all.\NYou don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:12.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:729875,732211}Here, this is your salary.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.33,0:12:15.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734338,735798}It's more than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.79,0:12:17.84,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735798,737841}You've done extra work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.84,0:12:20.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:737841,740219}Looks like Elroy\Ntook that into account.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.30,0:12:23.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:741303,743347}Thanks. See you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.05,0:12:25.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:744056,745432}Thanks for everything today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.43,0:12:26.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745432,746225}No problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.98,0:12:32.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750980,752398}This is bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.39,0:12:36.36,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752398,756360}He seems to have forgotten\Nto put Brock's part on the slip.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.11,0:12:39.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:757111,759071}In the end, Elroy makes mistakes\Nlike everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.98,0:12:42.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759989,762908}Now because of it,\Nmy salary's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.70,0:12:46.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:763701,766328}I can't celebrate\Nmy wife's birthday…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.12,0:12:51.70,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:770124,771709}What to do?
Comment: 0,0:12:54.54,0:12:54.54,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:774545,774545}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.88,0:13:04.59,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:782886,784596}Literally, just like my husband.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.23,0:13:14.23,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793230,794231}I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.48,0:13:15.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:794481,795441}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:18.65,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796233,798652}What do you mean, you lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.65,0:13:20.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:798652,800904}Well, I just told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:23.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:800904,803324}Lost all your salary!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.32,0:13:26.49,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:803324,806493}But what are you going to do\Nabout Mom's birthday tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:28.78,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:806493,808787}Well, that's why… I mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.78,0:13:30.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:808787,810998}Where did you drop it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.99,0:13:32.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:810998,812291}Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.29,0:13:34.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812291,814335}That's not the problem here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.00,0:13:37.83,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815002,817838}That's not the problem?\NWhat do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.83,0:13:40.00,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:817838,820007}You don't even know\Nwhere you lost it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:43.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820007,823802}I've been waiting for you the entire day.\NWhere have you been the whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:45.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823802,825971}U-Uh, what can I say…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.97,0:13:48.22,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:825971,828223}What is Mom to you, even?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.22,0:13:49.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:828223,829099}John?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.35,0:13:52.97,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830351,832978}We can't do anything\Nnow that it's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.56,0:13:54.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:833562,834396}But…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.39,0:13:56.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834396,836565}The bath is ready.\NGo get yourself cleaned up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.56,0:13:57.39,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836565,837399}Bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.39,0:13:58.73,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:837399,838734}You're all black.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.44,0:14:00.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839443,840110}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:03.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840611,843947}Why? Why are you\Nalways like this, Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:07.74,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:843947,847743}You always let yourself get distracted\Nand forget about truly important things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.66,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847743,848660}John.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.66,0:14:13.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:850662,853791}It's fine. I'll go look for it myself.\NLet's go, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.66,0:14:16.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:855667,856877}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.50,0:14:22.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:861507,862716}He looked serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.71,0:14:26.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:862716,866136}It seems he was trying\Nto do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.42,0:14:30.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:867429,870933}I understand.\NSo that's why he was so angry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:34.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:871809,874561}It's also because you're\Nso terrible at lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.56,0:14:35.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874561,875646}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.64,0:14:42.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875646,882194}Even a kid can see through a clumsy lie\Nlike this. You know what I'm talking about.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.19,0:14:44.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882194,884196}But I didn't lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.78,0:14:48.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884780,888075}I'll bet you just used the money\Nto help someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.07,0:14:48.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888075,888826}No…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.82,0:14:50.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888826,890202}The bath is ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.20,0:14:51.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890202,891412}All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.41,0:14:54.33,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:891412,894331}I can't believe boys sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.33,0:14:57.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894331,897292}By boys, you mean also me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.29,0:14:58.21,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:897292,898210}Who else, silly?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.66,0:14:59.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:898669,899878}I see…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.04,0:15:03.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901046,903048}Lassie, you're a dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.09,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:903048,906093}You can pick Dad's smell\Nand recover his money, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:10.88,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:907344,910889}The money must be somewhere\Nwhere he went.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.88,0:15:11.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910889,911640}Let's look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.05,0:15:14.64,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:913058,914643}Good. Good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.14,0:15:21.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:917146,921275}Oh? That's the wrong direction.\NMy Dad's company is on the hillside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.40,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922443,924403}Maybe I asked too much of her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.19,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924403,926196}John Carraclough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.19,0:15:31.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927197,931952}Sam didn't go the usual way\Nwhen he returned home today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931952,934037}You should trust Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.03,0:15:36.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934037,936290}Dad went… some other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937332,938208}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.04,0:15:40.16,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:939042,940169}Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.63,0:15:46.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943630,946675}Did Dad come here\Nwhen he came back from work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.43,0:16:02.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957436,962816}I see. It was tough for him to go home\Nright away, so he's been wandering around.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.82,0:16:13.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:970824,973243}Hey Lassie, if you go this way…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:21.37,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:979249,981376}Oh, I'm so full.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.37,0:16:25.96,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:981376,985964}To think that this place is so lively\Nall thanks to the salaries I had delivered.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.09,0:16:29.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987090,989176}Hello. You have my thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.59,0:16:34.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:989593,994181}I'm talking about the salary. I never imagined\NI'd get paid for my overtime today. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.22,0:16:38.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:996225,998560}You're a good soul,\Njust like Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.56,0:16:42.27,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:998560,1002272}It's an honor to work with people who can\Ntruly appreciate their employees' hard work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.73,0:16:44.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1002731,1004775}That's all I wanted to say.\NHave a good night.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.23,0:16:49.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007236,1009446}Looks like you're popular, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.73,0:16:50.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1009738,1010697}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:51.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011031,1011865}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.49,0:16:56.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012491,1016954}I wonder who he was?\NI feel like I've seen him before.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.87,0:17:01.95,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1017871,1021959}He's one of the miners.\NThere are no other people here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.21,0:17:15.55,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1031218,1035556}My Dad was so dirty.\NI can't believe he went to the market.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.22,0:17:22.52,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1040227,1042521}He's been circling here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.52,0:17:26.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1042521,1046316}Does that mean that he lost\Nthe money before coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.02,0:17:28.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1047025,1048026}That way?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:34.03,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049236,1054032}But if the money fell here,\Nit'll be hard to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.92,0:17:47.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066920,1067754}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.65,0:18:14.86,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1092654,1094865}Why did Dad come here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.36,0:18:18.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096366,1098327}Ah, keep it away, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:20.07,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1098327,1100078}Okay! Hey, Lassie.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.07,0:18:22.58,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1100078,1102581}Bad girl. Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:30.71,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107044,1110714}Get your dog out of my stand!\NI can't believe this town.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.71,0:18:32.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1110714,1112633}Now a window-shopping dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:37.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1112633,1117262}Just after a man covered in coal\Ncame and touched my brooches.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:38.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117262,1118930}Sir…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.93,0:18:40.30,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1118930,1120307}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.30,0:18:43.18,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120307,1123185}About the man covered in coal…\Ncould you describe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.18,0:18:47.31,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1123185,1127314}What can I say?\NHe was all dirty, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.31,0:18:51.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1127314,1131610}He wanted to get a brooch\Nand said he'll pay me next Friday.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:55.94,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1132027,1135947}He said that he wanted to give\Nan expensive gift to his woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.94,0:18:58.61,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135947,1138617}I told him to bugger off!\NIt's not for free, for crying out loud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.33,0:19:11.67,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1149336,1151672}Hey, Lassie…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.21,0:19:16.17,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152214,1156176}I'm no longer angry with Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:21.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1157636,1161473}In the end, Dad wanted\Nto make Mom happy, just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.28,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178073,1179282}A thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.78,0:19:41.82,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179783,1181827}Catch him!\NHe just picked a man's pocket!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.32,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1181827,1183328}Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.24,0:19:47.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1186248,1187040}Thief!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.04,0:19:48.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1187040,1188750}A thief?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.83,0:19:51.04,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1189835,1191044}I don't have my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.29,0:19:52.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1191294,1192754}He's there! Catch him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.67,0:19:57.34,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1193672,1197342}Follow him!\NHe might've stolen Dad's money!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.22,0:20:01.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200220,1201513}Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.76,0:20:06.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1204766,1206560}Is he the thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.47,0:20:09.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1207477,1209104}Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.69,0:20:18.69,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1213692,1218697}I can't believe this town.\NNow a thief steals my wallet!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.11,0:20:21.90,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1219114,1221908}I'm really sorry, Mr. Carraclough.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.90,0:20:23.20,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1221908,1223201}It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.57,0:20:27.53,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1223577,1227539}I'll tell the manager\Nto open the safe tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.53,0:20:31.79,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1227539,1231793}It's fine. It's not like\Nwe're starving or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.79,0:20:32.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1231793,1232919}Uh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.91,0:20:38.75,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1232919,1238759}But because of my miscalculation,\Nyou had to pay from your own money…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.75,0:20:41.63,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238759,1241636}I feel very bad about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.63,0:20:45.47,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1241636,1245474}That's enough. I feel bad about\Ndumping my work on you as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.47,0:20:47.85,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1245474,1247851}I'll see you on Monday.\NGood night.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:52.56,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249603,1252564}I knew it.\NAs expected, you used it for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.56,0:20:53.89,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252564,1253899}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253899,1255609}You're such a humble man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.31,0:20:57.77,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256318,1257778}We're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.77,0:21:00.11,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1257778,1260113}Dad, come here for a bit.\NJust come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.41,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1262908,1265410}I couldn't find the money,\Nbut check this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.41,0:21:06.87,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1265410,1266870}That's… How did you?…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1266870,1268914}You wanted to give\NMom a gift, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.74,0:21:11.91,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1270749,1271917}What's gotten into you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274461,1275420}Let's go, Lassie!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:17.29,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1276213,1277297}Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.92,0:21:20.80,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277923,1280801}I'll prepare the feast\Nfor your birthday tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.21,0:21:23.42,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281218,1283428}So don't worry\Nand have a good rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.72,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1285180,1287724}Looks like he's thought\Nof something again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.72,0:21:30.43,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1287724,1290435}"Don't worry, I'll prepare\Nthe feast for you", huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.43,0:21:33.60,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1290435,1293605}Isn't it nice?\NI'm sure looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.10,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1293980,1296107}You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.03,0:21:44.44,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1302030,1304449}Good grief.\NWhat an abominable town.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.44,0:21:46.99,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1304449,1306993}I let that kid choose a reward\Nfor catching the thief,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.99,0:21:50.24,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306993,1310247}and he had to choose\Nthe most expensive brooch!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.95,0:21:53.50,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310956,1313500}I'm never going back\Nto this place again.
