Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:01.13,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319714,1321132}{\i1}Today is Saturday.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.13,0:22:04.26,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1321132,1324261}{\i1}It's a day off for everyone,\Nbut not for the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.26,0:22:07.51,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324261,1327514}{\i1}All right, Lassie.\NLet's go to the lake today!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.51,0:22:10.93,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1327514,1330934}{\i1}We're going to fish\Nfor Mom's feast!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.93,0:22:13.81,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1330934,1333812}{\i1}Next episode:\N"6 Miles In Search For Food".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.81,0:22:15.02,lassie default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1333812,1335021}{\i1}Be sure to watch!
